item.title: Iron Ranger 8085 - Copper Rough & Tough Boots
item.description: Disclaimer: I'm not paid to write about this post, this is purely my ownership experience using these boots! This one deserves to be mentioned and hence I'm writing this post! I don't normally like to write about or make videos about my boots, but I could not resist the temptation to make a video and write about my Red Wing Iron Ranger boots from Red Wing shoe company, Minnesota! I purchased a pair of Red Wing Iron Ranger boots from the Red Wing retail store in Amsterdam around early 2018, I absolutely love the way it wears.
